commit aa2771365dcb37365b5920b6193d919deacca8fd
Author: Ayrx <terrycwk1994@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Aug 12 16:12:16 2013 +0800

    Added in code to assign timeslots upon confirmation
    
    * Timeslot is assigned upon confirmation of the account through
      email.
    * If the account is from any country besides China, a timeslot will
      be assigned based on a first come, first serve basis.
    * Timeslot will be stored in the database using a millisecond format.
      Any part of the application that needs to display a nicely formatted
      time has to parse this millisecond format. This is made easy using
      the joda-time library.

