commit 44c1c74ee17106d57479af442a367e337fd4e939
Author: Ayrx <terrycwk1994@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Aug 12 11:03:08 2013 +0800

    Fixed a bug that occurs when email is changed twice in a single session.
    
    The bug was caused due to Shiro using the email address as the primary
    pricipal of the authenticated session. This causes issues if the email
    address is changed as Shiro offers no avenue for updating the pricipal.
    
    The bug is fixed by changing the authentication process to use the
    never-changing contestant_id primary key of the Student class.

