commit bfe86172439c90128351201b591841d5f85c9fbb
Author: Ayrx <terrycwk1994@gmail.com>
Date:   Wed Aug 7 10:46:24 2013 +0800

    Introduces the use of local storage into the application
    
    This commit is an attempt to reduce the number of RPC calls to the
    server. By caching the user's profile data locally using the storage
    space introduced with HTML 5, the number of RPC calls to retrieve
    the profile data is reduced.
    
    The code has been introduced in two screens, the ContestDetailsScreen
    as well as the ProfileScreen.

